Module sc2002OOP
Package sc2002OOP.obj.internshipapplicaton

Interface IApplication

All Known Implementing Classes:
InternshipApplication
public interface IApplication

Internship Application Contract Interface

This interface defines the mandatory contract for an internship application within the IPMS. It ensures all application objects possess the core attributes and methods necessary to track a student's submission to an internship opportunity.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Kee Kai Wen, Kelvin Tay Wei Jie, Koay Jun Zhi, Lim Jia Wei Jerald, Teo Kai Jie
